lude tourist and foreigner stay in hk would be at greater risk of being extradited to Mainland China under the proposed bill, and suggested that legislation was politically motivated.<br />\n<br />\nOn 9 June, protesters estimated to number from hundreds of thousands to more than a million marched in the streets but the government reject to scrap the law.<br />\n<br />\nthe extradition proposal could be used as a tool to intimidate critics of the Hong Kong or Chinese governments, peaceful activists, human rights defenders and could further expose those extradited to risks of torture or ill-treatment. In a joint statement issued alongside other journalists unions and independent media outlets, the Hong Kong Journalists Association said the amendment would &quot;not only threaten the safety of journalists but also have a chilling effect on the freedom of expression in Hong Kong.<br />\n&quot;所以懇請各位曾經對香港文化有認識或者黎過香港，又或尊重人權認為人人平等既各位，可以幫手請願各個政府有關注事件，利用國際關係同具體措施去對香港同中國政府進行施壓，特別月尾前會通過所以情況緊急，可以的話請幫忙廣傳。&quot;依段唔知點譯好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2185902/hong-kong-considering-changing-law-transferring-fugitives-so\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F2185902%2Fhong-kong-considering-changing-law-transferring-fugitives-so&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=74234ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2185902/hong-kong-considering-changing-law-transferring-fugitives-so</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fugitive_Offenders_and_Mutual_Legal_Assistance_in_Criminal_Matters_Legislation_(Amendment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFugitive_Offenders_and_Mutual_Legal_Assistance_in_Criminal_Matters_Legislation_%28Amendment&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=bad96595\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fugitive_Offenders_and_Mutual_Legal_Assistance_in_Criminal_Matters_Legislation_(Amendment</a>)_Bill_2019<br />\n重點係要請佢地幫手向各地政府請願先有用，所以可能大家都要做多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031f68c5503c8585477d4544bbd10fb3c8c5cd29","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:30:21.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"72d0544796fad5490d0866f9663e119e5153369b","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:57:04.000Z","msg":"有人整左英文版懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205415/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205415/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9747004a825986bc0679d7480a3413a534c46449","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:32:08.000Z","msg":"新圖<br />\n感謝須藤凜々花巴打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/seF4yCU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FseF4yCU.png&h=1a9905a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3rZ6XW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3rZ6XW.png&h=27269989&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDekRpC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDekRpC.png&h=955338d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bC45h4E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbC45h4E.png&h=db55f9d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDgvubk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDgvubk.png&h=03fd3d81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HjDUVRn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjDUVRn.png&h=792c39e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nlink(#16):<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205541/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https:/