yTime":"2019-06-12T00:27:48.000Z","msg":"得閒既每一輪幫手推推一次，同埋見到其他po有新既可以幫手搬，我驚我miss左d更新,感謝<br />\n時事台:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1204813/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1204813/page/1</a><br />\n旅遊台:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205217/page/1</a><br />\n校園台:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205544/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205544/page/1</a><br />\n娛樂台:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205523/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205523/page/1</a><br />\n動漫台:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205541/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205541/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"69d49cac92efc7c0034611b7770790c00eca924a","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a9db8bb66053885af66e7a8cca0e241265edae33","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"449e24a737d033549e9c986ced07698d49f2ba45","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"感謝民進黨蔡英文巴打提供部分內容韓文翻譯<br />\n<br />\n홍콩은 영국에서 주권을 반환받은 이후 자치적으로 운영되는 자치구입니다. 홍콩과 중국은 일국양제로 엄연히 분리된 정치체제입니다.<br />\n<br />\n그런데 지금 홍콩 정부는 한 신규 법을 통과시키려고 하고 있습니다. 범죄인 중국 송환 법은 홍콩 사람들의 생명권, 자유권, 재산권, 존엄권 및 행복 추구에 관한 각종 인권을 박탈할 것입니다. 게다가 이 법이 가결되면, 홍콩에 있는 누구나 이 법 때문에 중국으로 잡혀갈 수 있습니다. 홍콩에서 일하는 외국인들은 물론이고, 심지어 여행객까지도 말입니다.<br />\n<br />\n이것을 막기 위해 6월 9일, 100만 명 넘는 사람들이 표결 반대 시위를 했습니다. 하지만 홍콩 정부는 여전히 해당 법을 통과시키려고 합니다. 현 홍콩 정부는 중국정부가 지정한 인사들로 이뤄져 있기 때문에 중국 정부의 명령을 따르고 있습니다. 따라서 각국의 정부가 국제 관계를 활용해서 홍콩의 기본 인권을 보호하도록 홍콩과 중국 정부를 압박하는 것이 필요합니다.<br />\n<br />\n홍콩 문화에 관심이 있거나 홍콩에 와본 적이 있으신 분, 그 외에도 인권을 중요하게 생각하시는 여러분, 각국 정부가 본 사건에 관심을 가질 수 있도록 도와주세요. 각국 정부가 국제 관계를 활용하여 구체적인 조치를 취해 홍콩과 중국 정부를 압박할 수 있도록 요구해주세요. 홍콩의 기본 인권을 보호할 수 있도록 관심을 가져주세요.<br />\n<br />\n현재 홍콩 정부는 이번 달 내로 해당 법을 통과할 계획입니다.<br />\n<br />\n혹시 가능하신다면 이 내용을 공유 부탁드립니다. 감사합니다.<br />\n<br />\n內容包括：<br />\n香港由英國返還主權之後，成為自體管理的自治區，與中國以一國兩制嚴格分離管理的政治體制。<br />\n<br />\n過去香港和中國大陸是不同的體制，但香港政府於今天有機會通過一條法例，從而令任何人在香港，即使是旅客、工作中的外國人都會有機會被捉回大陸。6月9日有103萬人上街遊行，但香港政府仍然堅持通過。這條例會剝奪香港人的生命權、自由權、財產權、尊嚴權及追求幸福的各項人權。由於香港政府聽命於中國內地政府，所以需要各國政府動用國際關係去保護香港現存的人權。請各位曾經對香港文化有認識或者來過香港，又或尊重人權的各位，可以幫忙請願各國政府關注事件，利用國際關係和具體措施去對香港和中國政府進行施壓。現時香港政府堅持在本月通過法例。可以的話請幫忙廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩左韓國朋友幫手proofread , 睇下會唔會有用。<br />\nlink(#27):<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205523/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205523/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"02a3a72d954aa071ff1ed18b81cb64291c2aaaff","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"sayasaya巴打upload 左日文版懶人包係twitter方便retweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/manameharuko/status/1138647420651261952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanameharuko%2Fstatus%2F1138647420651261952&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=bd626f73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanameharuko%2Fstatus%2F1138647420651261952&h=1501a005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/manameharuko/status/1138647420651261952</a><br />\nlink #26:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205541/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205541/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"d30f333da4f3997175336647338f278f6bd3fd2d","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02a3a72d954aa071ff1ed18b81cb64291c2aaaff","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"sayasaya巴打upload 左日文版懶人包係twitter方便retweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/manameharuko/status/1138647420651261952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanameharuko%2Fstatus%2F1138647420651261952&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=bd626f73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanameharuko%2Fstatus%2F1138647420651261952&h=1501a005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/manameharuko/status/1138647420651261952</a><br />\nlink #26:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205541/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205541/page/2</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"更新依個先岩:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sk00608/status/1138298616873795584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsk00608%2Fstatus%2F1138298616873795584&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=8a0f30b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsk00608%2Fstatus%2F1138298616873795584&h=8a32eb73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sk00608/status/1138298616873795584</a>"},{"pid":"6e301630281563d39f600915d7371b4e9a87f6e9","tid":1204813,"uid":51132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fa110d81ee3a864b68ca47b4ec93810614c9a828","tid":1204813,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"純種廢青巴打整左個英文版既範本:<br />\nStarting from tomorrow, any foreign tourists who come to Hong Kong would bear the risk of being arrested and extradited to Mainland China.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong is known for famous local movie stars like Bruce Lee and Jackie Chan. It is a place where permeates oriental ambiance with exquisite night view, a place vastly distinct from the neighboring mainland China. Hong Kong has long been ruled under a different political system from Mainland because of the &quot;One country, two systems&quot; constitutional principle. Yet, the high degree of autonomy enjoyed by the city could soon become water under the bridge. Tomorrow, the Hong Kong government may pass an extradition bill which exposes tourists or foreigners who work in Hong Kong to the danger of being shipped to Mainland China because of obscure reasons. <br />\n<br />\nOn 9 June, there were one million protesters took to the street in opposition to the extradition bill yet the Hong Kong government still insisted to pass the law. The extradition bill could be used as a tool to exploit Hong Kong citizens&rsquo; fundamental rights and it is not under the scrutiny of any human rights law.<br />\n<br />\nSince the current Hong Kong government is a puppet of the Mainland government, we desperately need the intervention of foreign governments to protect the declining human rights in Hong Kong and in the 21st century. We are here to solicit people who know and care about Hong Kong, or those who value human rights and equality to help draw your government&rsquo;s attention to this critical situation, or, if possible, ask them to pressure the Hong Kong and Mainland government through international relations and other different measures. This is an urgent call for help as the law is supposed to be passed by the end of this month. Please help spread this message. Thank you.<br />\n<br />\nlink:#33<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1205217/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1205217/page/2</a>"}]}